<br>
<br>
1.  Press Alt-O to bring up the options menu.  Click on the &quot;display&quot; tab.<br>
2.  Turn off all spell effects.<br>
3.  Turn off the 3-d sky effects.<br>
4.  Pull your clip plane slider all the way to the left.<br>
<br>
<br>
That's it.  You should now be able to move around relatively lag free...even with 400+ people in the zone.<br>
<br>
